snippet.title: I Caught A FISH and it was AFRAID!?!? [ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER - FISH FEAR ME]
snippet.description:
WISHLIST TODAY: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3000120/FISH_FEAR_ME/

FISH FEAR ME is a bullet heaven roguelike fishing game where you catch fish, fight them, sell their bones, and use the money to catch more fish! Upgrade your boat and weapons, hunt down sea monster bounties, and become the greatest battle-fisherman of all time!
